CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1960, pg. A9 reads: "Third Prize - The Music and Arts Club table won third prize, featuring fancy salads and chiffon pie. Left to right: Mrs. Maudelina Johnson, president; Mrs. Pearl Anderson, Miss Jessie Wallace and Mrs. Geneva Medley, club chairman at the Brotherhood Food Festival. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Maudelina Johnson, Pearl Anderson, Jessie Wallace, and Geneva Medley standing behind the Music and Arts Club table during Brotherhood Food Festival, Penn Sheraton Hotel, another version
